Merge contrast results coming from two different model.

Source: R/ContrastsInterface.R
merge_contrasts_results.Rd

Typically used with results of Contrasts and ContrastsMissing

merge_contrasts_results(prefer, add, modelName = "mergedModel")

Arguments

prefer

contrasts to use preferentially

add

contrasts to add from if missing in prefer

modelName

name of the merged model default "mergedModel"
